1.00	Brotherhood_of_mutants	Brotherhood of Mutants	The Brotherhood of Mutants, originally known as the Brotherhood of Evil Mutants, is a fictional Marvel Comics supervillain team devoted to mutant superiority over normal humans. They are among the chief adversaries of the X-Men. The original Brotherhood was created by writer Stan Lee and artist/co-writer Jack Kirby and first appeared in X-Men #4 (March 1964).	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/c/cd/Brotherhoodmute.jpg/250px-Brotherhoodmute.jpg
